1
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:48,850
This is the Phoenix Seal of the Li Kingdom.

2
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:49,820
I give it to you.

3
00:01:53,479 --> 00:01:54,810
Your Majesty once said,

4
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:56,100
that a woman's life

5
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:58,039
need not be confined to the palace.

6
00:01:58,039 --> 00:01:59,700
She can have her own pursuits.

7
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:01,880
My wish

8
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,620
is to ride into battle,

9
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,220
defend my country,

10
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:07,120
and achieve great deeds.

11
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,650
If you want to ride into battle,

12
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,180
I will not stop you.

13
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,220
If you want to defend the country,

14
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:17,960
then go.

15
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,210
Whatever you want to do,

16
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,730
I will not stand in your way.

17
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,040
But I am petty.

18
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:29,520
I cannot be the kind of Empress

19
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,760
who shares her husband with others.

20
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:34,160
I, Li Yunxi, swear here,

21
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,200
wholeheartedly,

22
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,320
for all my life,

23
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,280
you will be my only woman.

24
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,400
I see you always wear this jade pendant.

25
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,730
You must really like it.

26
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,840
Let it be our token of love.

27
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:07,760
This jade pendant

28
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,770
was given to me by my mother.

29
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:10,600
Li Yunxi.

30
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,760
If you put it on,

31
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,880
you can never take it off even if you die.

32
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:15,720
All right.

33
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:34,320
Empress, what are you doing?

34
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,120
Now you know fear?

35
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:39,960
It's too late.

36
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:42,840
I'm here to take revenge,

37
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,040
and settle old scores.

38
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:47,640
When the Late Emperor was alive,

39
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,200
he forbade the harem from

40
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:51,300
using Qingsirao to vie for favor.

41
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,680
That's just ordinary healing medicine.

42
00:03:57,480 --> 00:04:00,520
Consort Xue, née Liu, ignored the Late Emperor's ban

43
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:02,320
and brought shame upon the harem.

44
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:04,960
Today, I will sever the tendons in your hands and feet

45
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,000
as a punishment.

46
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:07,320
Don't you dare!

47
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,120
If you dare hurt me,

48
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,850
His Majesty will not spare you.

49
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:11,480
Do it.

50
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,480
Help!

51
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:16,240
Help!

52
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,160
Help!

53
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,440
Help!

54
00:04:22,280 --> 00:04:23,540
Help me, Your Majesty!

55
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,240
Stop!

56
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:28,560
Your Majesty,

57
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,880
I was wrongly accused.

58
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:33,560
Please bring justice for me, Your Majesty.

59
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,520
As the master of the Six Palaces,

60
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,000
how can you use lynching?

61
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,840
I am merely following the late Emperor's instructions

62
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:43,570
to punish concubines who misuse the Love Potion.

63
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:48,540
But there was no need to sever her hand and foot tendons.

64
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:50,360
It only makes you look ruthless.

65
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:53,880
To prevent the Empress from escaping the palace,

66
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,340
I severed her hand tendons

67
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,000
and foot tendons.

68
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,680
Yes.

69
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:02,320
I am ruthless.

70
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,480
Your Majesty,

71
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,400
I know I was wrong.

72
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:13,240
Please forgive me.

73
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,200
Since you know your mistake,

74
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,320
then rise.

75
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:25,440
Thank you for your mercy, Your Majesty.

76
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:35,050
Since you don't believe I'm innocent,

77
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:39,159
let's get a divorce.

78
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,080
Marrying me,

79
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,320
do you regret it?

80
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:44,840
Yes.

81
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,720
The biggest regret of my life

82
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:50,480
is marrying you

83
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,659
and coming to this prison of a palace.

84
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,440
Then who do you want to marry?

85
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,720
Li Yunmo?

86
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:59,680
If I had a second chance,

87
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,760
I'd rather marry Li Yunmo

88
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,440
than you.

89
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:11,160
Even if we torture each other,

90
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,620
we're staying together for life.

91
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:15,960
You're crazy.

92
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,160
Yes.

93
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,680
I am crazy.

94
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,640
If you want to leave me,

95
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,210
it will be over my dead body.

96
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,120
You want me to stay?

97
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:34,120
I would rather die.

98
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,970
His Majesty and Consort Xue

99
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:57,680
are truly deeply in love.

100
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,540
Their bond is stronger than gold.

101
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,200
That damned Xiao Ling.

102
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:32,020
How does she seem to predict everything?

103
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:33,880
My Lady,

104
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:36,360
didn't His Majesty come to save you?

105
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,480
It shows he cares about you.

106
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:42,240
As long as the Empress is alive,

107
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:45,480
His Majesty will never have eyes for me.

108
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:48,520
Xiao Ling, just you wait.

109
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,480
I wonder why Your Majesty

110
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:54,840
summoned me here.

111
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:56,960
It is good news.

112
00:07:58,320 --> 00:07:59,320
Good news?

113
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,560
Help me leave the palace,

114
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,760
and you will be the future Empress of Li.

115
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:08,440
You are willing to give up your position as Empress and leave?

116
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,760
Security is tight.

117
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:11,080
If I want to leave,

118
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,850
I can only rely on your help.

119
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,120
I agree.

120
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,050
Don't be afraid.

121
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,000
Halt.

122
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,520
By His Majesty's decree, without a token,

123
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:37,580
no one is allowed to leave the palace.

124
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,760
I have informed His Majesty

125
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:41,919
that I am visiting my family at Prince Qi's Manor.

126
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:43,320
Greetings, Consort Xue.

127
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:43,960
But,

128
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:46,340
I still need to search your carriage.

129
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:47,880
Search it.

130
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,960
She is my maid.

131
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:57,610
Must you search her too?

132
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,640
We wouldn't dare.

133
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,120
Let them pass.

134
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,520
Li Yunxi,

135
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,360
goodbye forever.

136
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:16,800
Stop her!

137
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:18,570
Quick! Stop her!

138
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,320
Consort Xue,

139
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,280
there is an assassin in the carriage.

140
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:21,200
If she gets away,

141
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,930
can you bear the consequences?

142
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,900
Hanxing, let's go.

143
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,800
The assassin is disguised as the Empress!

144
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:29,200
Anyone who kills her gets a reward!

145
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:29,680
Go.

146
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,000
Empress,

147
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:33,880
only with you dead

148
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,840
will His Majesty be truly mine.

149
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,000
Hanxing.

150
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,060
Keep shooting!

151
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,200
Kill them!

152
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,080
Stop!

153
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,480
Don't hurt her.

154
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:55,400
Go.

155
00:09:56,560 --> 00:09:57,080
No.

156
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:02,140
If Your Highness won't leave,

157
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:05,170
I'll have to threaten you with my life.

158
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:10,120
Hanxing.

159
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,680
Stay alive.

160
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,640
Your Majesty.

161
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:26,240
The Empress wanted to use my identity to leave the palace.

162
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:26,920
I refused,

163
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,280
so she knocked me out.

164
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,580
After I woke up,

165
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,000
I rushed here to stop her,

166
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,850
but I was a step too late.

167
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:33,800
Su Kuang.

168
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:34,840
Your Majesty.

169
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:36,780
It's not safe outside the palace.

170
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,700
Don't let anything happen to her.

171
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,900
Yes, Your Majesty.

172
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:42,880
Ling.

173
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,840
How could I ever hurt you?

174
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,920
You are my only wife.
